    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1. 问题背景"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Chery T1P换了新硬件，装车后发现升级功能不能用，导致需要去现场拆车线刷。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2. 问题分析"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "user-0e05a 分析总结了此次的原因, 如下："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "RE CHERY TIP9.15 升级问题分析与Lesson Learn .msg"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/18_%E5%9B%A0bootloader%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E6%8B%86%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84LessonLearnt/image-2023-9-21_10-14-8.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/18_因bootloader问题导致现场拆机的LessonLearnt/image-2023-9-21_10-14-8.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "3. 解决办法"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "MCU侧：软件出了优化方案，不再读pin状态（CPU_RESET_OUT_B_3V3）"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/18_%E5%9B%A0bootloader%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E6%8B%86%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84LessonLearnt/image-2023-9-22_15-40-20.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/18_因bootloader问题导致现场拆机的LessonLearnt/image-2023-9-22_15-40-20.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "4. 解决状态"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Chery所有分支都已同步",
        "zeekr已同步"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "5. 复盘 && 总结"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "扩展一下，如何避免现场拆机？"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "之前的项目，有哪些原因导致的去现场拆机的？",
        "以后如何避免现场拆机"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "初步总结一下："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "当发生以下case时："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "新sample",
        "修改BM/修改BL",
        "修改Memory Layout/存FLASH的数据（UCB）"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "需要："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "需要FO重点关注",
        "如果硬件改动，需要拉LCM&&BL同事review 硬件的changelist.",
        "需要丰富的测试（旧版本，新版本必须是服务器上生成的版本）"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "休眠唤醒 升级 旧版本升级到新版本 新版本自升级"
      ]
    }
